Sokolnik  is a farm in the administrative district of Gmina Młynary, within Elbląg County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately  west of Młynary,  north-east of Elbląg, and  north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn. The farm has a population of 3.
